(d) the Law is this Law of Security 2024 made by the Ruler;   
(e) the Regulations are legislation made by the DIFCA under the Law and are binding in nature;   
(f) Guidance is indicative and non-binding and may comprise practice guidance made and issued by the Registrar under the Law; and   
(g) references to “legislation administered by the DIFCA” are references to DIFC Law and rules or regulations made under such law conferring functions and powers on the Board of Directors of the DIFC Authority.
